											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Back to the young NOBLEMAN, who shrinks from the darkness and turns to Astarion, hope in his eyes. Astarion smiles and beckons him forward into the light - before laughing and digging his fangs into the boy's neck. (NOTE: Both Astarion and nobleman's silhouettes needs to be very clear here)" />
